metadata.name: Leapin Leprechauns
metadata.description: Leapin’ Leprechauns is a collection of 5,000 randomly generated pixel art collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Each Leapin’ Leprechaun is created from over 140 characteristics celebrating Ireland, Irish Culture and the NFT community. Your Leprechaun will grant you future benefits including exclusive Irish collectables and access to the fairy village.
